00:20:13,212 --> 00:20:15,005
I sincerely promise you

290
00:20:15,088 --> 00:20:17,799
that I'll only report the truth
and never lie to you.

291
00:20:18,300 --> 00:20:19,301
For JBC News…

292
00:20:19,384 --> 00:20:20,636
This is Song Ki-baek.

293
00:20:25,682 --> 00:20:27,809
God, what am I going to do now?

294
00:20:27,893 --> 00:20:31,146
What are you talking about?
We have so many things to do.

295
00:20:31,230 --> 00:20:34,566
Just get them together in one place,
and we'll have tons of things to do.

296
00:20:35,234 --> 00:20:37,152
"We Live Together."
This will work, I'm telling you.

297
00:20:37,236 --> 00:20:38,445
But the thing is--

298
00:20:38,528 --> 00:20:40,447
Think young people prefer to live alone?

299
00:20:40,530 --> 00:20:42,950
Kids these days are lonely
and want to be around people.

300
00:20:43,033 --> 00:20:44,826
That emotional ambivalence…

301
00:20:44,910 --> 00:20:47,955
-We'll satisfy their conflicting needs.
-Hey, emotional what?

302
00:20:48,038 --> 00:20:49,414
Be quiet.

303
00:20:49,498 --> 00:20:52,167
-I get that, but--
-It's okay if it feels familiar.

304
00:20:52,251 --> 00:20:55,337
If the setting and cast are different,
we can craft fresh stories.

305
00:20:55,420 --> 00:20:56,880
Hey, Ms. On.

306
00:20:59,258 --> 00:21:00,384
What did the chief say?

307
00:21:04,554 --> 00:21:06,014
Don't add or take out anything.

308
00:21:06,098 --> 00:21:07,557
Tell me verbatim.

309
00:21:09,726 --> 00:21:13,772
"It's outdated. She's lost her touch.
No one will want to be on the show."

310
00:21:17,401 --> 00:21:18,610
Me?

311
00:21:21,613 --> 00:21:24,074
Shake, shake, shaking my head.
I'm hopping mad.

312
00:21:24,157 --> 00:21:25,450
Shall I go ballistic on her?

313
00:21:26,451 --> 00:21:28,829
-What?
-It's "Shake, shake, I'm so mad.

314
00:21:28,912 --> 00:21:30,622
