00:29:11,207 --> 00:29:12,876
Song Ki-baek isn't screwed--

447
00:29:14,919 --> 00:29:17,172
I'm screwed.

448
00:29:17,797 --> 00:29:18,798
It's not working.

449
00:29:20,341 --> 00:29:23,344
Man, it's not working. What is going on?

