00:29:28,057 --> 00:29:29,392
DONKEYS THE DODGEBALL KINGS

452
00:29:29,476 --> 00:29:30,310
What is this?

453
00:29:30,894 --> 00:29:32,145
It worked, right?

454
00:29:32,228 --> 00:29:33,605
It did work a few times.

455
00:29:36,733 --> 00:29:37,984
Mr. Song Ki-baek!

456
00:29:38,067 --> 00:29:39,569
-Have you lost your mind?
-Oh?

457
00:29:40,487 --> 00:29:43,156
Ki-baek. What are you doing?

458
00:29:48,328 --> 00:29:49,412
WRITER ON WOO-JU

459
00:29:52,081 --> 00:29:53,082
Where are you?

460
00:29:53,666 --> 00:29:54,667
What?

461
00:29:55,502 --> 00:29:56,920
